ллл Quantum Break uses streaming videos for it's live action sequences.     ллл
ллл That means that you have to allow game to access internet access - the  ллл
ллл same way you in some games can access multiplayer or LAN access.        ллл
ллл                                                                         ллл
ллл Furthermore, even if you wont allow cracked material to allow internet  ллл
ллл access, you will get a "unable to steam" message screen, with a "skip   ллл
