ллл                                                                         ллл
ллл We're sure that eventually someone will come up with a "streaming movie ллл
ллл patch", but expect it to be really huge in size. Only the XBOX ONE got  ллл
ллл access to those live movie sequences offline - and the size of those    ллл
ллл are over 76GB, but the PC does not have access to such a feature.       ллл
ллл Therefore the game isn't incomplete, as those live sequences can still  ллл
ллл be access in online mode or skipable in offline mode.                   ллл
