ллл In the aftermath of a split second of destruction that fractures time   ллл
ллл itself, two people find they have changed and gained extraordinary      ллл
ллл abilities.                                                              ллл
ллл One of them travels through time and becomes hell-bent on controlling   ллл
ллл this power. The other uses these new abilities to attempt to defeat     ллл
ллл him  and fix time before it tears itself irreparably apart.            ллл
ллл Both face overwhelming odds and make dramatic choices that will         ллл
ллл determine the shape of the future. Quantum Break is a unique experience ллл
ллл one part hard-hitting video game, one part thrilling live action show,  ллл
ллл featuring a stellar cast, including Shawn Ashmore as the hero Jack      ллл
ллл Joyce, Aidan Gillen as his nemesis Paul Serene and Dominic Monaghan as  ллл
ллл Jacks genius brother William. Quantum Break is full of the vivid       ллл
ллл storytelling, rich characters and dramatic twists Remedy Entertainment  ллл
ллл are renowned for. Your choices in-game will affect the outcome of this  ллл
ллл fast-paced fusion between game and show giving the player a completely  ллл
ллл unique entertainment experience.                                        ллл
